name: ROYAL AIR FORCE Airbus A400M 'Atlas' in Action at Calgary Airport!
description:
Last weekend, Calgary got this special visitor from the Royal Air Force, the first one in quite a few months!

Normally, we get a good number of RAF aircraft coming through Calgary thanks to the training that they do in Southern Alberta.

Obviously that's not a thing at the moment, or at least not on the pre-2020 scale, but it's great to see the Brits again! Enjoy this A400M footage!
